title: Lumiere de Sel Natural Shape Himalayan Crystal Salt Lamp
description: This Salt Crystal Lamp is handcrafted, mounted on a wooden base, and includes an electrical cord and bulb. It is made of salt crystal that is ethically harvested from the geological range of the Himalayan Mountains, where salt deposits were formed millions of years ago. Due to its natural formation, each lamp is a uniquely beautiful combination of pink, orange and white – no two are the same! This lamp naturally produces negative ions, which help clean and purify the air. Ions are small electrically charged particles contained in the air we breathe. Other natural ion producers are trees and waterfalls. These lamps are helpful for people suffering from asthma and/or upper respiratory problems by reducing the amount of airborne bacteria and dust.
